@{b}1. System Requirements@{ub}

 An Amiga with sufficient memory  ( > 2Mb recommended)
 Kickstart & Workbench 2.04
 MUI Release 3.6

@{b} Libraries AlbIn_MUI wants to have:@{ub}

 Amigaguide.library v34+  If Not There Will Be No Online Help or Guide Preview


